  <summary>Sets the <property tag="lockColorMap">lockColorMap</property> <glossary tag="property">property</glossary> to false, causing the screen to be <glossary tag="redraw">redrawn</glossary> with the new <glossary tag="color table">color table</glossary> every time the <glossary tag="color table">color table</glossary> is changed.</summary>
